metadata.description: 2023 Wishing Echo Genesis is an artwork created with the help of my crypto friends during the Lunar New Year, inspired by the top communities, crytpto influencers, whales and industry leaders. I would like to thank all players in crypto who have been through the bear markets and not yet left the industry. This is the the best thing I can do to show my support.
